            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>mirin</strong>, <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame oil</strong>,<strong> rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> in a bowl and give it a good mix – this is your <strong>zingy</strong> <strong>marinade</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1689676865546-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1689676865546-x400.jpg",
