          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1689676865546-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1689676865546-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1689676865546-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut 2 A3 size sheets of <strong>baking paper</strong> (or tin foil) per person</p><p>Lay each <strong>hake fillet</strong> in the centre of the 2 sheets (doubling it up prevents any leakages!) and add to a baking tray</p><p>Spoon the <strong>zingy</strong> <strong>marinade </strong>evenly over the hake</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1689676869106-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1689676869106-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1689676869106-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1689676869106-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1689676869106-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Scrunch the edges of the <strong>baking paper</strong> together around the fish to form sealed parcel[s]</p><p>Put the baking tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until cooked through – this is your <strong>zingy hake en papillote</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1689676873816-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1689676873816-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1689676873816-x700.jpg",
